PrecisAmendments to the INDUSTRIAL DESIGNS RULES adding a new section intitled "Interpretation" clearly defining certain terms, improving accessibility to the Office to allow for oral representations at times, providing for more designated delivery points for deposit of documents across Canada, and establishing a method to determine the precise delivery date of a document to the Office.
